{"id":406953654,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"2 years, 11 months","timestamp":1602343767,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"4 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/406953654/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"String to Integer (atoi)","memory":"7.3 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int myAtoi(string s) {\n        int sign = 1;\n        int itr = 0;\n        long int res = 0;\n\n        bool firstD = false;\n        bool symbol = false;\n        while (itr < s.length())\n        {\n            if (!isspace(s[itr]) && !isdigit(s[itr]) && s[itr] != '-' && s[itr] != '+')\n                return 0;\n            \n            if (isspace(s[itr]) && symbol)\n                return 0;\n            \n            if (s[itr] == '+' || s[itr] == '-')\n            {    \n                if (!symbol)\n                    symbol = true;\n                else\n                    return 0;\n\n                if (s[itr] == '-')\n                    sign = -1;\n            \n            }\n            \n            \n\n\n            if (isdigit(s[itr]))\n            {\n                firstD = true;\n                for (int i=itr; i<s.length(); i++)\n                {\n                    if (!isdigit(s[i]))\n                        break;\n                    \n                    res = res * 10 + (s[i] - '0');\n                    if (res * sign > INT_MAX)\n                        return (int) INT_MAX;\n                    if (res * sign < INT_MIN)\n                        return (int) INT_MIN;\n                }\n                \n                break;\n            }\n            itr++;\n        }\n        \n        res = sign * res;\n        \n        if (res > INT_MAX)\n            res = INT_MAX;\n        if (res < INT_MIN)\n            res = INT_MIN;\n        \n        return (int) res;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"string-to-integer-atoi","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
